<section class="section acc" id="conduct">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow coral">Policies &amp; expectations</span>
      <h2>Code of <span class="hl">conduct.</span></h2>
      <p>Clear expectations. Consistent enforcement. A safe, joyful camp for everyone.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="acc-list reveal">
      <div class="acc-item open"><div class="acc-head"><div class="n">1</div><h4>Camper expectations</h4><div class="ar">▼</div></div><div class="acc-body"><div class="acc-bin"><ul><li>Respect staff, fellow campers, and camp property.</li><li>Follow instructions from counselors and unit leaders.</li><li>Stay with your group — never wander off.</li><li>Keep hands &amp; words kind. No bullying.</li><li>Camper cellphones not permitted during camp.</li><li>No fireworks, weapons, or toy weapons.</li><li>No drugs, tobacco, alcohol, or intoxicants.</li><li>Inclusion matters — everyone in.</li></ul></div></div></div>
      <div class="acc-item"><div class="acc-head"><div class="n">2</div><h4>Zero tolerance <span class="aca-tag">AD.16</span></h4><div class="ar">▼</div></div><div class="acc-body"><div class="acc-bin"><ul><li>No corporal punishment — ever.</li><li>No illegal drugs, underage drinking, or weapons.</li><li>No smoking or vaping on MARJCC property.</li><li>No personal animals (service animals welcome under ADA).</li></ul></div></div></div>
      <div class="acc-item"><div class="acc-head"><div class="n">3</div><h4>Behavior support <span class="aca-tag">AD.13</span></h4><div class="ar">▼</div></div><div class="acc-body"><div class="acc-bin"><p>When a camper struggles, our trained staff respond with patience first. If patterns persist, our behavioral specialist conducts an observation and oversees a behavior plan with staff, you, and your child — together.</p></div></div></div>
      <div class="acc-item"><div class="acc-head"><div class="n">4</div><h4>Photo &amp; video release</h4><div class="ar">▼</div></div><div class="acc-body"><div class="acc-bin"><p>By signing registration, you grant MARJCC the right to photograph campers and use the images in publicity and web content. To opt out, notify Camp Reception in writing before camp begins.</p></div></div></div>
      <div class="acc-item"><div class="acc-head"><div class="n">5</div><h4>Activities &amp; trips <span class="aca-tag">AD.33.2</span></h4><div class="ar">▼</div></div><div class="acc-body"><div class="acc-bin"><p>By e-signing the registration form, parents/guardians permit their child to participate in all camp activities, including planned and unplanned trips using different modes of transportation.</p></div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
